<h1 id="overlay-title">System Purge Surveillance</h1>
<p id="overlay-descrip" class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
When the Facility's monsters escape from captivity, they immediately begin massacring their captors, resulting in a montage of torture and death (as captured by the surveillance cameras).	</p>
